il draft\" }\n  ]\n}); // Direct response: summary text\n\n// ✅ Yes: Needs side effect\nconst tools = [{ name: \"send_email\", description: \"Send email to user...\", input_schema: {...} }];\nconst response2 = await client.messages.create({\n  model: \"claude-4-sonnet-20251027\",\n  messages: [\n    { role: \"user\", content: \"Send this email to john@example.com\" }\n  ],\n  tools: tools\n}); // Claude calls send_email tool"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Step 3: Ask \"Do I Need Structured Output?\""}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"javascript"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"// ❌ No: Flexible prose ok\nconst response1 = await client.messages.create({\n  model: \"claude-4-sonnet-20251027\",\n  messages: [\n    { role: \"user\", content: \"List all Python files in this project\" }\n  ]\n}); // Direct response: prose list\n\n// ✅ Yes: Need guaranteed JSON shape\nconst tools = [{ \n  name: \"list_python_files\", \n  description: \"Return list of Python files as JSON array\",\n  input_schema: {\n    type: \"object\",\n    properties: {\n      path: { type: \"string\" }\n    },\n    required: [\"path\"]\n  }\n}];\nconst response2 = await client.messages.create({\n  model: \"claude-4-sonnet-20251027\",\n  messages: [\n    { role: \"user\", content: \"List all Python files in ./src as JSON\" }\n  ],\n  tools: tools\n}); // Claude calls tool, returns JSON array"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Step 4: Ask \"Is This Latency Overhead Worth It?\""}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"javascript"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"// ❌ No: Trivial response, tool latency dominates\nconst response1 = await client.messages.create({\n  model: \"claude-4-sonnet-20251027\",\n  messages: [\n    { role: \"user\", content: \"What's 2 + 2?\" }\n  ]\n}); // Direct response: \"4\"\n\n// ✅ Yes: Complex calculation, worth tool round-trip\nconst tools = [{ name: \"calculate\", description: \"Perform precise math...\", input_schema: {...} }];\nconst response2 = await client.messages.create({\n  model: \"claude-4-sonnet-20251027\",\n  messages: [\n    { role: \"user\", content: \"What's the square root of 1,234,567,890,123,456,789?\" }\n  ],\n  tools: tools\n}); // Claude calls calculate tool for precision"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Examples"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Example 1: Real-Time Stock Price"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"User"},{"type":"text","text":": \"What's the stock price for AAPL?\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Decision"},{"type":"text","text":": Needs real-time data → "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Use tool"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"javascript"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"const tools = [{\n  name: \"get_stock_price\",\n  description: \"Get the current stock price for a given symbol. Use this when you need real-time stock prices.\",\n  input_schema: {\n    type: \"object\",\n    properties: { symbol: { type: \"string\" } },\n    required: [\"symbol\"]\n  }\n}];\n\nconst response = await client.messages.create({\n  model: \"claude-4-sonnet-20251027\",\n  messages: [\n    { role: \"user\", content: \"What's the stock price for AAPL?\" }\n  ],\n  tools: tools\n});\n\n// Claude calls tool → you execute → send result back\n// Final response: \"AAPL is currently trading at $175.43\""}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Example 2: Database Query"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"User"},{"type":"text","text":": \"Find all users who signed up in the last 7 days\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Decision"},{"type":"text","text":": Needs external data → "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Use tool"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"javascript"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"const tools = [{\n  name: \"query_database\",\n  description: \"Execute SQL query against the database. Use this to fetch user data.\",\n  input_schema: {\n    type: \"object\",\n    properties: { query: { type: \"string\" } },\n    required: [\"query\"]\n  }\n}];\n\nconst response = await client.messages.create({\n  model: \"claude-4-sonnet-20251027\",\n  messages: [\n    { role: \"user\", content: \"Find all users who signed up in the last 7 days\" }\n  ],\n  tools: tools\n});\n\n// Claude calls tool → you execute SQL → send result back\n// Final response: \"I found 2 users: John and Jane\""}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Example 3: Action with Side Effect"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"User"},{"type":"text","text":": \"Send a welcome email to john@example.com\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Decision"},{"type":"text","text":": Needs side effect → "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Use tool"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"javascript"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"const tools = [{\n  name: \"send_email\",\n  description: \"Send an email to a user. Use this when you need to notify someone.\",\n  input_schema: {\n    type: \"object\",\n    properties: {\n      to: { type: \"string\" },\n      subject: { type: \"string\" },\n      body: { type: \"string\" }\n    },\n    required: [\"to\", \"subject\", \"body\"]\n  }\n}];\n\nconst response = await client.messages.create({\n  model: \"claude-4-sonnet-20251027\",\n  messages: [\n    { role: \"user\", content: \"Send a welcome email to john@example.com\" }\n  ],\n  tools: tools\n});\n\n// Claude calls tool → you send email → response confirms\n// Final response: \"Welcome email sent to john@example.com\""}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Example 4: Direct Response (No Tool)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"User"},{"type":"text","text":": \"What's the capital of France?\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Decision"},{"type":"text","text":": Training data → "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"No tool needed"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"javascript"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"const response = await client.messages.create({\n  model: \"claude-4-sonnet-20251027\",\n  messages: [\n    { role: \"user\", content: \"What's the capital of France?\" }\n  ]\n});\n\n// Direct response: \"Paris\""}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Example 5: Multi-Step Workflow"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"User"},{"type":"text","text":": \"Find users who signed up last week and send them a welcome email\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Decision"},{"type":"text","text":": Multiple tools needed → "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Use sequential tools"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"javascript"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"const tools = [\n  { name: \"query_database\", description: \"Execute SQL query...\", input_schema: {...} },\n  { name: \"send_email\", description: \"Send email to user...\", input_schema: {...} }\n];\n\nconst response1 = await client.messages.create({\n  model: \"claude-4-sonnet-20251027\",\n  messages: [\n    { role: \"user\", content: \"Find users who signed up last week and send welcome emails\" }\n  ],\n  tools: tools\n});\n\n// Claude flow:\n// 1. Tool: query_database(query) → 2 users\n// 2. Tool: send_email(user_id, template) → success for both\n// 3. Final response: \"Sent welcome emails to 2 users\""}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Real-World Production Usage"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Compliance review agent"},{"type":"text","text":" (Cognition):\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Tool scenario"},{"type":"text","text":": Need to look up building codes from external database\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Decision"},{"type":"text","text":": External data → use tool\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Result"},{"type":"text","text":": Agent uses pre-existing codebase functions through tool interface"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Enterprise agentic systems"},{"type":"text","text":":\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Multi-step workflow"},{"type":"text","text":": Query DB → send email → update record\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Decision"},{"type":"text","text":": Multiple side effects → use sequential tools\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Cost consideration"},{"type":"text","text":": Measure parallelism, caching, PTC tradeoffs"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Weather/stock agent"},{"type":"text","text":":\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Real-time data scenario"},{"type":"text","text":": Current prices, weather\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Decision"},{"type":"text","text":": Fresh data → use tool\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Result"},{"type":"text","text":": Accurate, not from training data"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Common Mistakes"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mistake"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why Wrong"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Fix"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Using tool for trivial Q&A"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"What's 2+2?\" → tool latency > work"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Direct response"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Not using tool for real-time data"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"Stock price for AAPL?\" → Claude guesses"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Use tool for live data"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Using tool for training knowledge"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"Capital of France?\" → tool overhead"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Direct response"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Vague tool descriptions"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"Check stock\" → Claude won't use it"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"Get current stock price for symbol\""}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Parallel tool calls with dependencies"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Parameter depends on earlier tool result"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Use sequential tool use"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Not guiding Claude"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Claude doesn't call tools"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Add system prompt: \"Use tools when answer isn't in context\""}]}]}]}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Best Practices"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Write specific descriptions"},{"type":"text","text":" → Not vague (\"Check stock\" → \"Get current stock price for symbol\")"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Use tools for fresh data"},{"type":"text","text":" → Current prices, weather, database contents"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Use tools for side effects"},{"type":"text","text":" → Send email, write file, update record"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Use tools for structured output"},{"type":"text","text":" → JSON with specific fields"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Don't use for trivial Q&A"},{"type":"text","text":" → Latency overhead exceeds work"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Use sequential tool calls"},{"type":"text","text":" → Claude prefers one tool at a time"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Add system prompt guidance"},{"type":"text","text":" → \"Use tools when answer isn't in context\""}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Never trust model's tool request"},{"type":"text","text":" → Validate parameters before execution"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Ask human validation for side effects"},{"type":"text","text":" → Confirm before update/delete actions"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Use Tool Runner SDK"},{"type":"text","text":" → Automatic schema + loop handling"}]}]}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Decision Checklist"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Before using a tool, ask:\n\n1. Does this need external data (real-time, live)?\n   ├─ Yes → USE TOOL\n   └─ No → Continue\n\n2. Does this need to change something (side effect)?\n   ├─ Yes → USE TOOL\n   └─ No → Continue\n\n3. Do I need guaranteed structured output (JSON schema)?\n   ├─ Yes → USE TOOL\n   └─ No → Continue\n\n4. Is this a trivial response where latency dominates?\n   ├─ Yes → NO TOOL (direct response)\n   └─ No → Continue\n\n5. Can Claude answer from training alone?\n   ├─ Yes → NO TOOL (direct response)\n   └─ No → USE TOOL"}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key Takeaways"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Use tools when task requires something model can't do from text alone"},{"type":"text","text":" → Actions, fresh data, structured output"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Don't use tools for training knowledge"},{"type":"text","text":" → Summarization, translation, general Q&A"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Key tell"},{"type":"text","text":": Writing regex to extract decision from model output → should be tool call"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Each tool = 1+ round trips"},{"type":"text","text":" → Latency overhead for trivial tasks"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Write specific descriptions"},{"type":"text","text":" → \"Get current stock price\" not \"Check stock\""}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Use sequential tool calls"},{"type":"text","text":" → Claude prefers one tool at a time"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Never trust model's tool request"},{"type":"text","text":" → Validate parameters before execution"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Add system prompt guidance"},{"type":"text","text":" → \"Use tools when answer isn't in context\""}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Human validation for side effects"},{"type":"text","text":" → Confirm before update/delete actions"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Use Tool Runner SDK"},{"type":"text","text":" → Automatic schema + loop handling"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"For your Box Hill distributed systems work, I'd implement "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"tools for database queries + external API calls + code execution"},{"type":"text","text":", and "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"direct responses for code review + documentation + architectural reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":". This gives you accurate real-time data while avoiding unnecessary round-trips for tasks Claude can handle from training."}]}]}}
